{"name":"Dracula","nameCn":"德古拉","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/ba/9f/10845_crt_OGLit.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>德古拉</li><li><span>别名: </span>德拉库拉</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ドラキュラ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>The Impaler</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>&quot;穿刺公&quot;弗拉德三世</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Vlad III Tepes</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ヴラド3世・ツェペシュ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>伯爵</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>大公</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>生日: </span>11月13日</li><li><span>种族: </span>吸血鬼</li>","detail":"德古拉，原型来自外号为“穿刺公”的中世纪人物‧瓦拉几亚大公弗拉德三世，他在1456年至1462年间统治现在的川西凡尼亚地区。<br />当时的敌军奥斯曼土耳其人曾在德古拉城堡前看见两万人被插在长矛上任由其腐烂，被这令人作恶的景象吓得拔腿就跑，就连领军的拜占庭征服者穆罕默德二世自己也无法接受这种景象；“穿刺公”之名由此而来。也正因为如此，弗拉德在其死后被人传为吸血鬼；罗马尼亚的川西凡尼亚地区也就此成为吸血鬼的摇篮。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/962","name":"悪魔城ドラキュラ ~蒼月の十字架~","nameCn":"恶魔城 苍月十字架","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/5c/93/962_w4ebI.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":4},{"href":"/subject/61213","name":"Hotel Transylvania","nameCn":"精灵旅社","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/4a/bd/61213_4IbNf.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Adam Sandler","castHref":"/person/16158","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/79/ed/16158_prsn_c4PNC.jpg","type":2},{"href":"/subject/208708","name":"Castlevania Season 1","nameCn":"恶魔城 第一季","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/26/e3/208708_DEN2F.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"内田直哉","castHref":"/person/3888","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/97/25/3888_seiyu_anidb.jpg","type":2},{"href":"/subject/260405","name":"コナミ ワイワイレーシング アドバンス","nameCn":"科乐美赛车","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/84/41/260405_r0pDN.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":4},{"href":"/subject/1339","name":"悪魔城ドラキュラ ジャッジメント","nameCn":"恶魔城 审判","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d1